Add a *path operation* using an HTTP DELETE operation.
## Example
```python from fastapi import APIRouter, FastAPI
app = FastAPI() router = APIRouter()
@router.delete("/items/{item_id}") def delete_item(item_id: str): return {"message": "Item deleted"}
app.include_router(router) ```

Add a *path operation* using an HTTP OPTIONS operation.
## Example
```python from fastapi import APIRouter, FastAPI
app = FastAPI() router = APIRouter()
@router.options("/items/") def get_item_options(): return {"additions": ["Aji", "Guacamole"]}
app.include_router(router) ```
